n Forschungsergebnisse der letzten sechs Jahrzehnte umfassend berücksichtigt.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn Greek, Ancient (to 1453).0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aFictionvGeneral. 0aMan-woman relationshipszItalyzSyracusevFiction. 0aSlaveszTurkeyzCariavFiction. 7aHISTORY / Ancient / General.2bisacsh1 aReardon, Bryan P., eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Classics and Near East Studies 2000 - 2014z9783110636178oZDB-23-GCN0 cprintz978359871277740uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311095732740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110957327423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110957327/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GCNc2000d2014